data.name: treeNode3.Tag
data.value:
Artillery Novice's effects:

+10% damage to Cannon and Ballista shots.

+15% raw to Crag S, Triburst S, Wyvern S, and Cannon S.

+30% damage to Impact Phial bursts from CB.

+10% Fire to GL shots, and -33% heat generation from GL shots and Wyvern's Fire.

Artillery Expert's effects: 

+20% damage to Cannon and Ballista shots.

+30% raw to Crag S, Triburst S, Wyvern S, and Cannon S.

+35% damage to Impact Phial bursts from CB.

+20% Fire to GL shots

-50% heat generation from GL shots and Wyvern's Fire.

-25% cooldown on Wyvern's Fire.

data.name: treeNode6.Tag
data.value: Bloodbath Soul is a combination of Attack Up (L) and Evasion +2. It provides +20 Attack and +0.2 seconds of additional invincibility when dodging.\n\nTrue Bloodbath Soul additionally provides Composed, which grants a +10% charge rate for all Hunter Art, Valor, and Alchemy Gauges.

data.name: treeNode7.Tag
data.value:
When in Green, you get +10% raw. In Yellow, +15%. In Orange or Red Sharpness, you get +20%. 

 Originally in Gen, the values did not scale and were instead flat bonuses. Green granted +10 raw, Yellow +15, and Red/Orange +20. 

 Warning, dipping into Yellow and below causes the Low Sharpness Modifier to kick in, reducing your damage by up to 40%. Please see the associated entry in the glossary for more details on the LSM.

data.name: treeNode8.Tag
data.value: Boltreaver Soul provides a combination of Critical Boost, Bonus Shot, and Sharpness +1. Together, they grant +15% damage on critical hits, increasing the critical hit damage from 1.25x to 1.4x, increasing the shots fired from Rapid Fire volleys by one, and 25 more units of Sharpness, as long as the sharpness of the weapon can be increased.\n\nTrue Boltreaver Soul additionally adds On Alert, which increases your Hunter Art, Valor, and Alchemy Gauges whenever you take damage.

data.name: treeNode15.Tag
data.value:
Critical Eye -3: -15% Affinity. This is added to the negative portion of Chaotic weapons.

Critical Eye -2: -10% Affinity. This is added to the negative portion of Chaotic weapons.

Critical Eye -1: -5% Affinity. This is added to the negative portion of Chaotic weapons.

Critical Eye +1: +10% Affinity. This is added to the positive portion of Chaotic weapons.

Critical Eye +2: +20% Affinity. This is added to the positive portion of Chaotic weapons.

Critical Eye +3: +30% Affinity. This is added to the positive portion of Chaotic weapons.

data.name: treeNode17.Tag
data.value:
Combines Negate Stun and Challenger +2.

Completely negates the infliction of stun.

+20 Attack and +15% Affinity while a monster in the same area is enraged.

True Deadeye Soul additionally adds Fortify, which grants +10% Attack and +15% Defense when you cart, stacks up to two times. You must cart, not your teammates, to activate this effect.

data.name: treeNode18.Tag
data.value:
When at or below 66% health, you gain several effects:

+10% raw.

All Elemental Resistances are set to 50, regardless of original amount.

Special Dragonblight that negates all other elements on your weapon aside from Dragon.

data.name: treeNode19.Tag
data.value:
Dragon Atk +1: +5%, then +4 Dragon damage, if your weapon has Dragon-element damage.

Dragon Atk +2: +10%, then +6 Dragon damage, if your weapon has Dragon-element damage.

Dragon Atk Down: -25% Dragon damage, if your weapon has Dragon-element damage.

data.name: treeNode20.Tag
data.value:
Combines the effects of Attack Up (L) and Windproof (Hi):

+20 Attack (flat).

Negates all wind pressure exerted from monsters, except for Dragonwind, which is reduced.

True Dreadking Soul additionally adds Adrenaline +1, which grants +15 Defense if at or below 40% Health.

data.name: treeNode21.Tag
data.value:
Combines the effects of Status Atk +2 and Wide-Range +2.

+25%, then +1 Status (Poison, Para, Sleep)

Spreads the effects of some items to everyone in the same area. Includes Mushrooms if you have Mushromancer, Potions, Herbs, Antidotes, Adamant and Might Seeds, and Nulberries.

True Dreadqueen Soul additionally grants Herbalist, which increases efficacy of Herbs to about 1.5x Potion level.

data.name: treeNode22.Tag
data.value:
Combines the effects of Adrenaline +2 and Scavenger.

+30% Attack, +45 Defense while you have 40% or less Health.

33% chance to recover 25 max Stamina when you consume a recovery item.

True Drilltusk Soul additionally grants Artillery Expert.

+20% damage to Cannon and Ballista shots.

+30% raw to Crag S, Triburst S, Wyvern S, and Cannon S.

+35% damage to Impact Phial bursts from CB.

+20% Fire to GL shots.

-25% cooldown on Wyvern's Fire.

data.value:

+10% Element (Fire, Water, Thunder, Ice, Dragon) damage, if your weapon had any of those.

+50% duration to items which have a duration. Extends sharpness effect of "Heavy Grinder" when using a whetstone.

+30% Bomb Damage (applies to all items with ‘bomb’ in their name)

100% chance to combine all ‘bomb’ items.

+10 Defense while a Hot Drink is in effect.

+20 Fire Res.

Guarantees that the monster will flee immediately once a Dung Bomb is applied, if the monster can be affected by Dung Bombs, and if it can flee.

Prevents Stench and Blastblight.

data.value:

+20% charge rate for GS, Hammer, Bow charge attacks, -20% charge rate for DB’s Demon Gauge, LS Spirit Gauge, SA Phial Gauge, and CB Phials.

True Redhelm Soul additionally grants Marathon Runner, which grants -50% Stamina usage when dashing or otherwise draining Stamina over time.

data.name: treeNode67.Tag
data.value:
For Blademaster weapons, after you perform evasive actions (5 rolls, 9 hops/dashes), restores 5 units of Sharpness. This effect does not stack with the Seregios Blademaster weapons.

For Bowguns (Light/Heavy), per evasive action, you have a 33% chance to load the currently selected shot type. This effect stacks with the similar ones provided by the Seregios LBG and HBG.

For Bows, applies a +50% damage increase when you use C.Range Coatings. This effect does not stack with the one provided by the Seregios line of Bows.

+20% Attack on Pellet S from Bowguns, +30% Attack on Spread-type Arrows from Bows.

+10% Attack on Pierce S from Bowguns and on Pierce-type Arrows from Bows.

When a monster is downed or otherwise immobilized, you get a yellow aura around your hand for 60 seconds. While this aura persists:

20% damage to HAs which have motion values and which are not listed below.

+20% duration to all HAs which have durations.

Arisen Phoenix: Heals more health.

data.value:
